WorkItem.Description:
I am generating Excel files using PHPExcel library (version 1.8.0, 2014-03-02). The file can be opened correctly but when I try to add a new worksheet by clicking "New Sheet" button on the bottom of the window I get this error message:

"That command cannot be used on multiple selections."

This occurs only if I have set Office2003 Compatibility mode on:

$objWriter->setOffice2003Compatibility(true);

If I remove this line or change parameter value to false adding new worksheet works.

Worksheet is not protected and I have not selected multiple cells on the worksheet. Only one cell is selected.

If I save the file with new name and open that new file adding new worksheets works fine.
WorkItem.Summary: "That command cannot be used on multiple selections" error occurs when trying to add a new worksheet on the Excel 2013
